beer.beer_description:
For four decades, Circus Oz has delighted generations of audiences across our country and the world. This Strong Pale Ale is a celebration of the incredible strength, extraordinary grace and rebellious spirit of Australia’s national circus. Hawkers is proud to support Circus Oz with a donation from every case sold.
As Ernest Hemingway once said,
“The Circus is the only fun you can buy that is good for you”

items.badge_description: Either you must be sampling or really like beer! That's 12 beers in 1 day.

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 15 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 4!

items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink any beer you have never had before on three Thursdays in a 30 day period!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 330 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 67!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 215 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 44!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 260 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 53!
